      size=2>One alternative is the <a href="http://schwab.ed10.net/ud/FSXF/5ZAF/1C0Q/PJ/UUL2JZ"> Schwab 1000 Fund&#174;</a>.  It&#146;s designed to help investors track the total return of the Schwab 1000 Index&#174;.  The index includes 1,000 large- and mid-cap stocks and will typically represent between 85% and 90% of the total value of all U.S. stocks.&nbsp;</FONT></P>
